creator: GO: Taxi rides in Zambia
descriptionHtml:
What is GO? GO is a mobile application that efficiently matches drivers with passengers,whether your are a private vehicle hoping to fund your dreams,or a taxi driver looking for the most efficient way to get a passenger. GO is the right partner for you.

GO: revolution of transportation in Zambia
GO mobile taxi app is an innovative startup based in Lusaka, Zambia. We match customers looking for a ride
with drivers. GO app sends a request to taxis in the area. Closest driver accepts the taxi order and pick up the the rider.

How to use GO taxi
1. Download the free app from the store
2. The app detects your current location and sends order requests from the passengers nearby
3. App shows you estimated price of the ride
4. After ride confirmation, passengers see you approaching on the map and has estimated time of arrival
5. Should you need to contact your client, you can find passenger's details in the order details
6. At the end of the ride you see ride total and can rate the trip

Our contacts
go.taxis23@gmail.com
260978584465
https://web.facebook.com/goforbusiness/
descriptionShort: Driver for GO and become your own boss

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: In this release, we’ve updated the user’s side menu to make it more clear.
